                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18410405-1183-offence-1 t18410405-cd-164"></join>2nd of April</rs>, 5lbs. weight of tobacco-leaf, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18410405-name-1063" type="victimName">
